To make it even easier for you to operate the Pirate Chain wallets, we have created a new easy wallet installation script.
This works for Pirate wallets (Windows) and offers: 

- Fast block syncing
- Bootstrap downloading
- Bootstrap extract
- Zcash parameters installation
- Auto-launch of wallet

How To Use The Script:

-Right CLick On Where You Have/Downloaded The Script File
-Permit The Script  (ex. chmod +x Sevenseas.sh)
-Execute The Script (ex. Sevenseas.sh)


What The Script Does:

-Wallet Downloading
-Fast block syncing 
-Bootstrap downloading
-Bootstrap extract
-Zcash parameters installation
-Auto-launch of wallet


